metadata.title: Story hoodie
metadata.visionDescription: The image features a stylized logo with the word "RAZOR" in bold, red letters against a black background. The letters are uneven and angular, giving an edgy, dramatic appearance. Above the word, there's a white, stylized letter "S" enclosed within a partial circle, resembling a logo or insignia. The overall style is bold and stark, with a high contrast between the black background and the red and white lettering, creating a striking visual impact.
